title: Ep. 144 “Retrogrades, Natal Charts, And Sextrology” ft. @IAmLivingAligned Gigi Robinson
description:
This week Gigi Robinson joins us to really breakdown astrology while taking a look at our own birth charts and tells us what you really need to know about the signs, compatibility, and how to use your chart as a guide. Lillith, retrogrades, Venus in Leo…if none of this makes sense to you take a listen as Gigi breaks it all down and explores our charts in depth.
